{"tid":2439344,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大家返工做過最柒嘅事俾人踢爆係咩","createTime":"2021-03-09T07:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T09:48:29.000Z","uid":130402,"like":38,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d8997f151313fb1b2c8283b1846782cc273b83fd","tid":2439344,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"第一份正職，要得閒落去派傳單，派大概半個幾鐘<br />\n<br />\n因為唔想派，佢叫我落去派嘅時候就直接去咗隔離餐廳食嘢，食食吓法國經理入咗黎買外賣，俾人直接踢爆<br />\n<br />\n俾佢照完肺，下一次派傳單都係唔想派，直接喺街度同人講「幫我攞一張掉咗佢唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」點知派派下咁啱派咗張傳單去一個好奇怪嘅人，佢有啲愕然咁望住我話你講咩，我就答佢「係呀掉咗佢得㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩晒」之後佢有啲不可思議咁樣答我「你點可以咁樣對客人講嘢！」我嚇咗一嚇，開始覺得有啲唔對路，之後佢話「公司啲傳單你係咁樣派㗎咩？阿Xyz(我經理個名）咁樣教你㗎？！」<br />\n<br />\n之後我即刻知道領野了，一定係高層，我屌，佢上咗去公司嘅時候我都即刻急步上去，執埋啲嘢話辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fa35ade7339aadf887fe84554cc1f0b94f4fe6","tid":2439344,"uid":122134,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"有無咁黑"},{"pid":"1bed8888db4f526845a098efbd103d36c40c755b","tid":2439344,"uid":90820,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"是但攝晒入附近啲信箱當派完咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f96acc64222e4e9641da6d49b588bedabea9e6","tid":2439344,"uid":122601,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柒到"},{"pid":"96b0995b371e2e621086cf9e09cc8db99206b13b","tid":2439344,"uid":130402,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1bed8888db4f526845a098efbd103d36c40c755b","tid":2439344,"ui